French vibes in USA .. 

📍 Forsyth Park Fountain, Savannah, Georgia, USA

* It's 150 year old fountain made on ideal French concept of having a fountain at the center of the park. 

* Although it's beautiful but it's not unique and the fountain was ordered from a catalog. 

* It's the most pictured scenery in Savannah, GA. People often do romantic proposals, wedding photo shoots here. 

*Needless to say, artists making live paintings, live music and the people strolling at ease, does give French vibes while being here. 

Save this to not miss the spot when in Savannah.

📍Tungnath temple, Chopta, Uttarakhand
🗓️ 10 August, 2020 

Pro tip: It you visit Tungnath, don't miss to hike up to see this amazing view from temple on top (Ganga Ji temple) at Chandrashila peak. This is also known as Moon rock as it's so close to the moon (feels like).
